comments.body:
The issue was not about not creating the field. It was about not mentioning the Context at all in this class. We removed it a while ago to make sure that we only depend on trees and that we could at some point generate an abstract `PositionPickler` that does not depend on the compiler. Having the contexts only invites for missuses of the contexts in this implementation.

```diff
-    treeAnnots: untpd.MemberDef => List[tpd.Tree])(using @constructorOnly ctx: Context) {
+    treeAnnots: untpd.MemberDef => List[tpd.Tree],
+    relativePathReference: String) {
```

